1 Para: Gp ← The DAG representation of a hybrid plan p
2 Para: M ← The cost model that estimates cost in seconds
3Para: α ← The visibility delay in the HTAP database
4 Function planSelection(DAGs,α)do
5bestPlan ← O; Costbset ←O;
6for each Gp in DAGs do
7Costp ← calculateCost(Gp,α);
8if bestPlan == O V Costp
9 bestPlan = p; Costbest ← Costp;
10return bestPlan;
11 Function calculateCost(Gp,α) do
12preCost ← O; exeCost ← estimateCost (Gp, M) ;
13inoalidSet ← findAllPendingTasks(Gp);
14subs ← removePendingTasks(Gp,invalidSet);
/* removePendingTasks returns the strongly connected components after removing pending
15tasks in Gp. */ foreach sub E subs do
16Costsub ← estimateCost (sub, M);
17if preCost
18return Cost ← exeCost +α -min {preCost,α};
